# OpenAI API key for the Knowledge Review page.
# Two ways to provide it:
#   1) Copy this file to .env.local (gitignored) and paste your key below, then `npm run dev`.
#   2) Or leave this unset and paste the key in-app: Knowledge Review → Settings (stored in your browser only).
# Note: with option 1 the key is inlined into the dev bundle — fine for local use, do NOT deploy a build with it.
VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
